product.name: Floor Mats & Cargo Liner for 2024 2025 Lincoln Nautilus All Weather Protection TPE Rubber Floor Liners for 2024 2025 Lincoln Nautilus Full Set Automotive Mat Accessories, Black
product.description:
Our Story
NIKALAIKA is a company specializing in the production and sales of auto accessories. Founded in 2001, our aim is to let customers buy the most reliable products with the least money and have a pleasant shopping experience! ! Our car floor mats can protect your car around the clock, keep your car clean and tidy, and provide you with the best driving experience.
Most Advanced Floor Protection
Our floor mats accurately and completely lines the interior carpet giving full interior protection!
Digital laser measurements of interior surfaces offer a consistently perfect fit!
For your safety, Professional installation recommended.
Include:
2 x front floor liners (driver’s & passenger’s side)
1 x 2nd-row floor liners
1 x trunk mat
NIKALAIKA car floor mat perfect fits front and rear row of the car based on scan original car data. So don't worry about jam accelerator, brake or front seat track questions.
The floor mat are made of TPE material, which have stronger toughness, durability and elasticity, wear resistance and scratch resistance advantages. What's important, it is nontoxic and odorless.
The rear floor liner is not only worn resistant but also remains flexible under extreme temperature. The state-of-the-art technological construction protects your vehicle’s floor from wear, dirt, and salt corrosion.
product.bullet_points:
• FIT PERFECT: NIKALAIKA floor mats and cargo liner compatible with 2024 2025 lincoln nautilus, no need trimming. Adopts 3D screening technology to capture every corner and crevice to offer perfect fit and coverage
• BUILT FOR DURABILITY: The all weather floor mats & trunk mat for 2024 2025 lincoln nautilus are made of TPE materials featuring waterproof, wear-resistant, non-slip and odorless. High tensity and safe TPE material keeps its flexibility in all season while still offering an excellent feel and extreme wear resistance
• ALL WEATHER PROTECTION & NON-SLIP: Our car mats for 2025 lincoln nautilus with uniquely designed channels and raised edge can effectively trap liquid, debris, snow, mud, and sand to keep your car and shoes clean; Built-in retainer clips to firmly grip the mat and prevent slipping when wet
• EASY TO CLEAN: The custom floor liners & cargo mat are waterproof, stain-resistant and easy to clean. Clean easily with a damp towel, or remove them from the car and rinse with water. Quick and easy to get your car floor mats looking nice and new again
• WORTH EVERY PENNY: Car mats accessories are processed with advanced technology, rendering tailored protection and all-weather guard to your vehicle; Available in a set with 2 x front floor mats & 1 x 2nd-row floor liners & 1 x cargo liner
